Author: cjisconfusing
Text: It's way easier for me to fast during the week bc I can easily make it through all of my classes without food and if I binge it will usually just be once at night. Weekends are so much harder bc I spend all my time alone in my room so I tend to fill the time with food. l kinda have no people to hang out with rn which is probably why I have been binging so much this school year.

Author: TheAdjunctTavore
Text: I literally make myself go do silly errands or try on clothes in stores in a fast. If I stay busy I can forget. Video games are a great distraction for me as well. My hands are busy so I can't stuff my face.
